Package com.vmware.appliance.networking

The com.vmware.appliance.networking package provides interfaces for managing network configuration of the appliance.

See: Description

Package com.vmware.appliance.networking Description

The com.vmware.appliance.networking package provides interfaces for managing network configuration of the appliance. The package is available starting in vSphere 6.5.
